me.leoko.advancedgui.utils

Class GuiItemInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.leoko.advancedgui.utils.GuiInstance
      • me.leoko.advancedgui.utils.GuiItemInstance

  • public class GuiItemInstance
extends GuiInstance
    The GuiItemInstance is a handheld GuiInstance using a map item to display a 1x1 Layout and the players gaze to control the cursor.
